---
const props = Astro.props;
---

<section id="registration">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 lg:px-8 py-24 sm:py-32">
    <div
      class="mx-auto max-w-5xl lg:text-center px-2 sm:px-6 lg:px-0 m-3 pb-12 pt-3 nm-flat-white-lg dark:nm-flat-gray-700-lg rounded-lg p-8 text-left sm:text-center w-full"
    >
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-2xl lg:text-center pt-24 px-6 lg:px-0">
        <h2 class="text-base font-semibold leading-7 font-Futurewave">
          please read
        </h2>
        <p
          class="mt-2 text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight font-Futurewave sm:text-4xl"
        >
          Important Notice
        </p>
      </div>
      <p
        class="mt-6 text-sm sm:text-lg leading-8 text-blue-950 dark:text-sky-500 font-Futurewave px-6 sm:px-8"
      >
        Apologies for any inconvenience. Please be aware that you'll need to set
        up your own development environment. See pre-requirements as per below!
        <br /><br />
        Due to time constraints, there won't be an opportunity for installation or
        troubleshooting during the workshop.
      </p>
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-2xl lg:text-center pt-24 px-6 lg:px-0">
        <h2 class="text-base font-semibold leading-7 font-Futurewave">
          Who's this for?
        </h2>
        <p
          class="mt-2 text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight font-Futurewave sm:text-4xl"
        >
          Well it is for you!
        </p>
      </div>
      <p
        class="mt-6 text-sm sm:text-lg leading-8 text-blue-950 dark:text-sky-500 font-Futurewave px-6 sm:px-8"
      >
        This free workshop is designed for aspiring developers or if you just
        want to know how to build a website!
      </p>
      <p
        class="mt-6 text-sm sm:text-lg leading-8 text-blue-950 dark:text-sky-500 font-Futurewave px-6 sm:px-8"
      >
        Learn how to build a blog/portfolio using Tailwind CSS and Hygraph, with
        a little dive / getting your feet wet, into the Astro framework.
      </p>
      <p
        class="mt-6 text-sm sm:text-lg leading-8 text-blue-950 dark:text-sky-500 font-Futurewave px-6 sm:px-8"
      >
        Enhance your understanding of modern web development while creating this
        blog/portfolio.
      </p>
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-2xl lg:text-center px-6 lg:px-0">
        <div class="p-0 sm:p-10 lg:flex-auto">
          <div class="mt-10 flex items-center gap-x-4">
            <h3
              class="flex-none text-sm font-semibold leading-6 font-Futurewave"
            >
              Pre-Requirements
            </h3>
            <div class="h-px flex-auto bg-sky-600"></div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex mt-8 space-x-3 leading-6">
            <svg
              class="h-6 w-5 flex-none text-sky-600"
              viewBox="0 0 20 20"
              fill="currentColor"
              aria-hidden="true"
            >
              <path
                fill-rule="evenodd"
